{"tid":2098500,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲更新旅遊警示 警告民眾在中國可能遭任意拘留","createTime":"2020-07-07T13:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T14:32:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d86cac00cdcce57677cfda5a96e2cfc3313536c","tid":2098500,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T13:55:45.000Z","msg":"澳洲更新旅遊警示 警告民眾在中國可能遭任意拘留<br />\n<br />\n澳洲外交部更新對中國的旅遊警示，指有外國人在中國因危害國家安全而被拘留，提醒澳洲民眾前往中國有被任意拘留的風險。澳洲理莫里森上周表示，政府因應港區國安法實施，正積極考慮向港人提供避風港簽證。<br />\n<br />\n 澳方今次公布，適逢清華大學法學院前教授許章潤，昨日在北京住所被警方帶走。許章潤曾發表文章批評中共取消國家主席任期限制，以及在疫情下中央政策令人民憤慨等。他是墨爾本大學法學院博士。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2345880&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivSq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=50a0bebf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2345880</a>"},{"pid":"b055f016a04907b24d5bb646da8e3c205806b31f","tid":2098500,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c8fb3956a7e702c364747ee3eee728884ea2e2","tid":2098500,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"好似好多國家都俾中國旅遊警示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留名睇石頭、腳同戰狼出現"},{"pid":"6b4ec04285be3ce8f8e67461d3ebb715656ae685","tid":2098500,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RLTx4sg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRLTx4sg.gif&h=d4bab4c5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}